# Blocked edit fallback (tee)

- If editor/ApplyPatch edits are blocked for a **text file** (e.g., filtered by `.cursorignore`, "Waiting for Review"), do **not** attempt ad-hoc shell edits.
- Use the tee heredoc fallback to overwrite the file and **re-read/verify** it.
- For **binary** files (e.g. compiled PDFs under `docs/reference/em-fields-pamphlet/`, generated PNGs/SVGs under `docs/hardware/visuals/`), never use the tee fallback — regenerate via the canonical build target (`make reference-pdfs`, `make electrician-pdfs`, etc.) instead.
